replies.body:
I personally hate when people 3v1 me while i'm splitpushing. I think it's a pussy thing to do. They walk up to me and pick a fight 1v1 so I get into it then BAM Thresh and Diana pop out of the jungle. I hate that shit.

So I started warding. Problem solved. Now if they want to gang bang me like the cowards they are I know to back off and let them learn that they are going to be wasting their time until they man up enough to fight a clean 1v1.

It's really that easy to do. {{item:3361}}
